      "content": "hey, im working on a brand strategy for a high-end luxury watchmaker—think patek philippe or rolex level. we need to nail down our \"ideal consumer\" persona for the upcoming global campaign. can u help me build a detailed profile? i need to know their lifestyle, their interests, but also their general ethnic and cultural background so we can make sure our imagery and marketing feel authentic to the \"luxury\" vibe. thanks.",
